						               													<description>Wise Alec is the family fun trivia game that plays to any crowd. Featuring a hilarious demonstration of trivia, tongue twisters, and sassy social strategy, Wise Alec picks up on players&amp;rsquo; clever choices, good manners, and a little luck to find the wisest owl on any family game night.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Playing Wise Alec, opponents have a chance for making wise choices before, during, and after the game. On each turn, players try to earn points as they move around the board answering questions in three different categories from elementary school curriculum. Each question offers a choice of an easy or more difficult question. Players can use their strengths for maximum or minimum risk and reward, but when a player lands on a Wise Alec card the fun really begins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The unique elements of Wise Alec offer a choice of two levels of difficulty on every turn and playing to win by points or time, make the game ideal for multi-generation game play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wise Alec was designed by educators to promote a healthy and active lifestyle, good manners, reinforce learning while ensuring each player&amp;rsquo;s ego remains intact as no one gets eliminated and no one feels like a fool.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wise Alec was awarded Dr. Toy&amp;rsquo;s 100 Best Children&amp;rsquo;s Products.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
